STATE
v.
Tyler Deion GREENFIELD 11A19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 24, 2019 Jess D. Mekeel, Assistant Attorney General, Ben R. David, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Kathryn L. VandenBerg, Assistant Appellant Defender, for Greenfield, Tyler Deion.

The following order has been entered on the Motion for Extension of Time to File Brief filed on the 21st of June 2019 by Defendant:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of June 2019."

Defendant shall have up to and including the 14th day of August 2019 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court.
